sentences: Gock is a featured composer on the scores for over 300 TV series, and together with his creative and business partner Dinesh Wicks has won the APRA AMCOS Screen Music Award for 'Most Performed Composer â€“ Australia' seven times (2020, 2019, 2018, 2017, 2015, 2012, 2011).
Gock and Wicks were recognized for their contribution to the Australian music industry in 2014 with the coveted APRA AMCOS International Achievement Award.
Gock and Wicks expanded the company to include US operations in 2012 with offices in New York and Los Angeles.
